Run Mongo in a Docker container

docker run --name mongo -p 27017:27017 -d mongo:3.3.10

Populate World collection

$ mongoimport --db hello_world --collection World --file ${PROJECT_ROOT}/src/test/resources/mongo_worlds

Populate Fortunes collection

$ mongoimport --db hello_world --collection Fortune --file ${PROJECT_ROOT}/src/test/resources/mongo_fortunes
